# Input

```svelte
{#await promise then [first, second, ...rest]}
<p>First: {first}, Second: {second}</p>
<p>Rest: {rest.join(', ')}</p>
{/await}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#await promise then [first, second, ...rest]}
	<p>First: {first}, Second: {second}</p>
	<p>Rest: {rest.join(', ')}</p>
{/await}

```
